title: BRIEF-PayPal says receives subpoena from U.S. DOJ related to anti-money laundering program | Reuters
text:
Market News | Wed Feb 8, 2017 | 5:07pm EST BRIEF-PayPal says receives subpoena from U.S. DOJ related to anti-money laundering program 
Feb 8 Paypal Holdings Inc : 
* Paypal Holdings-received subpoenas from U.S. Department of Justice seeking production of certain information related to historical anti-money laundering program 
* Paypal Holdings- cooperating with DOJ in providing information in response to subpoenas - SEC filing 
* Paypal Holdings - unable to predict the outcome of the government's investigation Source text - bit.ly/2kPljqm Further company coverage: Next In Market News Morning News Call - India, February 9
